DucksPhys is a 3D mini game aimed at 7-12 year-olds that teaches them the concepts of physics. Students can explore the laws of physics by balancing weights in form of ducks using their hand gestures which are being read by the Leap Motion Controller.

DucksPhys - Balancing physics with fun!

Check out the demo at: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wKcT2Rz5ZNI

